Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveChioma Avril Rowland the third baby mama of Nigerian music star, Davido, is celebrating her 27th birthday today, April 20, 2022.
Celebrating herself on her big day, the mum of one took to social to share gorgeous photos of herself.
In a post on her Instagram page, she wrote: “27 and gorgeous! I’m grown 
”
Chioma (ChefChi)
Chioma and Davido started dating in late 2017 and went exclusive the following year.
The music star proposed to her in 2019, days after their introduction.
They welcomed their son, Ifeanyi the same year.
